plot: Now that Rob's decided to stay in Dallas, Khloe gets a firsthand look at how out of control Rob's OCD has gotten. When he receives news that his living situation in LA is compromised, his repetitive compulsions quickly go from amusing to downright scary, and Khloe's attempts to make him realize that he has a problem fall on deaf ears. Meanwhile, Malika pays Khloe a visit only to find that she has to share her bestie with NBA wife, Porschla Kidd.
